  "response": "LendingTree is a legitimate online lending marketplace that has been in business since 1996. Here are some key points:\n\n1. Legitimate Business\n- Publicly traded company (NASDAQ: TREE)\n- Not a direct lender, but a loan comparison platform\n- Connects borrowers with multiple lenders\n\n2. How It Works\n- Users submit loan request details\n- Platform matches users with potential lenders\n- Lenders compete for your business\n- You can compare rates and terms\n\n3. Services\n- Mortgages\n- Personal loans\n- Auto loans\n- Credit cards\n- Student loan refinancing\n\n4. Pros\n- Free to use\n- Multiple lender options\n- Helps compare rates\n- Soft credit check initially\n\n5. Cons\n- May result in multiple hard credit inquiries\n- Not guaranteed loan approval\n- Some users report receiving many marketing calls/emails\n\n6. Safety\n- Uses encryption to protect personal information\n- Established reputation in the lending industry\n\nWhile legitimate, it's always recommended to:\n- Read reviews\n- Compare offers from multiple sources\n- Understand terms before accepting a loan\n- Protect your personal information\n\nOverall, LendingTree is a reputable service for comparing loan options.",
